data.description: ==>> OPEN HOUSE  4/27-4/28  (SAT - SUN)  10am to 1PM <<== Welcome to your charming ranch-style retreat, nestled in a tranquil cul-de-sac! * This inviting 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts a rare full basement, perfect for customization. The open floor plan, freshly painted interiors, and gleaming hardwoods create an ideal space for entertaining. Relax in the plush-carpeted primary bedroom with a private bathroom featuring dual sinks. The kitchen, with its island, is a culinary haven, while the laundry room offers convenience with washer, dryer, and storage. Park your vehicles in the oversized 2-car garage, recently painted. Enjoy the outdoors on the deck overlooking the landscaped backyard. Additional basement features include an extra bedroom/office, laundry room, and framed bathroom awaiting your touch. With parks, schools, and amenities nearby, and easy access to highways, this home offers both comfort and convenience. Experience suburban living at its finest in this move-in-ready gem!
